## Existing Implementation

### Fully Implemented (no changes needed)

| File | What it does |
|------|-------------|
| `packages/cli/src/index.ts` | Commander program with all 6 commands registered (`login`, `link`, `deploy`, `env`, `logs`, `rollback`) |
| `packages/cli/src/lib/api-client.ts` | `ApiClient` class with `get<T>()`, `post<T>()`, `delete()` methods, reads token from global config, sends `Authorization: Bearer {token}` header |
| `packages/cli/src/lib/config.ts` | Config management: `getGlobalConfig()` / `saveGlobalConfig()` for `~/.gblockparty/config.json`, `getProjectConfig()` / `saveProjectConfig()` for `.gblockparty/config.json` |
| `apps/dashboard/src/lib/api-helpers.ts` | `withAuth(handler)` middleware, `jsonResponse()`, `errorResponse()` helpers |
| `apps/dashboard/src/lib/auth.ts` | Session management with JWT creation, validation, cookie handling |

