## Steps

| # | Step | Key Deliverable |
|---|------|----------------|
| 1 | CLI API Routes | Server-side `/api/cli/deploy` and `/api/cli/env/:projectId` routes with token auth |
| 2 | Login Command | Browser-based OAuth flow with local callback server, token storage |
| 3 | Link Command | Interactive project selection, project config saved to `.gblockparty/config.json` |
| 4 | Deploy Command | Trigger deployment, stream build logs, print deployment URL |
| 5 | Env Pull/Push Commands | Download/upload env vars, mask secrets, `.env.local` file I/O |
| 6 | Logs Command | Fetch/stream build logs with `-n` and `-f` options |
| 7 | Rollback Command | List deployments, interactive selection, confirm and execute rollback |

